ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectJoseph Ignace David Dragon ** leasehold interest in an unsurveyed parcel of land **
PrecisOrder authorizing JOSEPH IGNACE DAVID DRAGON of Ottawa, Ontario, an employee of the Government of Canada, Department of Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada, to acquire a leasehold interest in an unsurveyed parcel of land in the Northwest Territories.
